  "title": "Xtra Buttery Russian Seed Pilaf",
  "description": "A buttery and energizing Russian dish featuring seeds, bhuna, and keto-friendly ingredients, cooked to perfection in a kazan cauldron. This pilaf is perfect for a hearty lunch or dinner.",
